/Calculus/ContDiff/Defs.html#ContDiff\">ContDiff</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Real/Basic.html#Real\">ℝ</a> <span class=\"fn\">(↑<a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Notation.html#Top.top\">⊤</a>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">u</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/MeasureTheory/Constructions/BorelSpace/Basic.html#OpensMeasurableSpace\">OpensMeasurableSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">X</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/MeasureTheory/Measure/Typeclasses/Finite.html#MeasureTheory.IsFiniteMeasureOnCompacts\">MeasureTheory.IsFiniteMeasureOnCompacts</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/MeasureTheory/Measure/MeasureSpaceDef.html#MeasureTheory.MeasureSpace.volume\">MeasureTheory.volume</a></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">h</span> : <span class=\"fn\">∀ (<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ι</span>), <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Mathematics/VariationalCalculus/HasVarGradient.html#HasVarGradientAt\">HasVarGradientAt</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">F</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">grad</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">u</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Mathematics/VariationalCalculus/HasVarGradient.html#HasVarGradientAt\">HasVarGradientAt</a> <span class=\"fn\">(fun (<span class=\"fn\">v</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">X</span> → <span class=\"fn\">U</span></span>) (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">X</span>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\">∑ <span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ι</span>, <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">F</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span> <span class=\"fn\